node.text:
Here’s a little sneak-peek of a drawing I’m working on! 🌼✨ Trying to get some practice drawing a dynamic pose and I’ve been having fun with it 🥰 full process video will go up on Patreon soon!✨ I can’t decide if she’s stretching or dancing, what do you think? 🤔

I make tutorials & drawing videos on my Patreon! 💌 Once you join you’ll get access to over 50+ tutorial videos & step-by-steps, real-time process videos, cozy draw with me videos, my custom brush set, studio vlogs, & more ✨ the link is in my bio! ☁️

#reels #artreels #drawing #drawingprocess #ipadpro #ipadproart #procreate #digitalart #painting #digitalpainting #characterdesign #characterart #oc #procreateart #procreatedrawing #illustration #ipaddrawing

node.text:
River study 🏞✨ Swipe to see my reference! I’m trying to practice drawing environments with a person in them, which is something I tend to avoid 🙈 but I want to get better at it so here we go! ☺️ I filmed the full drawing process for a real-time process video and it’s posted on my Patreon! 💌 Patrons get to see each step of the drawing process at a slower pace, see my full screen while I draw, how I work with brushes & layers, and more 🌻 The link is in my bio! What are you guys currently trying to improve in your work? ✨

I make tutorials & drawing videos on my Patreon! 💌 Once you join you’ll get access to over 50+ tutorial videos & step-by-steps, real-time process videos, cozy draw with me videos, my custom brush set, studio vlogs, & more ✨ the link is in my bio! ☁️

#environment #environmentart #environmentdesign #visualdevelopment #visdev #painting #digitalart #drawing #sketch #digitalillustration #digitalpainting #digitaldrawing #illustration #characterdesign #characterconcept #natureart #ipadproart #procreate

node.text:
Fox studies 🦊🌲✨ Here are the finished fox sketches from my reel the other day! I had so much fun studying foxes and learning more about fur and animal anatomy 🥰 Today I posted a new step-by-step tutorial on my Patreon about how to draw foxes with tips & techniques from start to finish! The link is in my bio if you wanna check it out 🌲🪵

I make tutorials & drawing videos on my Patreon! 💌 Once you join you’ll get access to over 50+ tutorial videos & step-by-steps, real-time process videos, cozy draw with me videos, my custom brush set, studio vlogs, & more ✨ the link is in my bio! ☁️

node.text:
Working on a sketch concept inspired by citrus fruits! 🍊✨ This is usually what my sketch looks like right before I’m about to add color & start rendering 😌 I’ve always found it helpful to do some grayscale shading before coloring to add some extra depth to the drawing! You can watch my sketching & shading tutorials on my Patreon 💌✨ link is in my bio! Do you like sketching or coloring more? ✏️

I make tutorials & drawing videos on my Patreon! 💌 Once you join, you’ll get access to over 50+ tutorial videos & step-by-steps, real-time process videos, PSD’s, my custom brushes, studio vlogs, and more 🪴 the link is in my bio! ✨
